description:
HOA is a short skateboarding film for Thank You Skateboards that was shot exclusively in the residential neighborhoods of Los Angeles County. The film is a nod to every skateboarder's early skateboarding experience of skating the often less than ideal terrain of their local neighborhood but making due nonetheless.
HOA was created as part of Transworld Skateboarding's SKATE & CREATE 2020 contest.
skateboarding.transworld.net/skateandcreate2020/
Featuring: Daewon Song & Torey Pudwill
Cameos: Chad Muska & Rodney Mullen
Directed, Shot, Edited: Colin Kennedy
Music used with permission: Nation of Language "The Wall & I"
title: HOA
